                  "content": [
                    {
                      "amount": 0,
                      "display_style": "card",
                      "ep_id": 7084,
                      "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/10/15/237301566/693da8a1b01352fde999598e49b34fde_541324707221914524.png",
                      "menu_id": 23,
                      "name": "Элементальные драконы",
                      "type": "custom_entry"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "Nibelung was the Dragon King, the leader of the elemental dragons and the primeval dragon that had been born alongside that world.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "amount": 0,
                      "display_style": "card",
                      "ep_id": 4897,
                      "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/10/08/237301566/513d51e0ebfd54f5da34a9f85dfaf61f_4818954959690057221.png",
                      "menu_id": 10,
                      "name": "Изначальный",
                      "type": "custom_entry"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "After losing the first war with the Heavenly Principles, Nibelung acquired the",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "from outside of this world and led the dragons in a fight against the order established by the outsiders. An unimaginable war took place in Teyvat, causing destruction on an unprecedented scale. In war, the victor would inherit the right to shape the world, while the losers must turn into ash.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "Voyager from a distant world",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "When the dragons ruled Teyvat, a voyager from a distant world was drawn to the light of Nibelung's world. She foresaw the death of this world and invited Nibelung to join her on a journey, but he refused to abandon his people. When the voyager returned to this world, Nibelung had already been defeated by the Primordial One and left the world to gain forbidden knowledge.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "amount": 0,
                      "display_style": "card",
                      "ep_id": 4913,
                      "icon_url": "https://act-webstatic.hoyoverse.com/event-static-hoyowiki-admin/2024/01/03/9750d15029b9018793ef9d9f0bfec6de_743071265959457769.png",
                      "menu_id": 10,
                      "name": "Апеп",
                      "type": "custom_entry"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "Even after the death of the Dragon King, the Dendro Dragon, Apep, did not give up on her attempts to change the course of history. She tried to gather new forbidden knowledge on the borders of a world that was hanging by a thread from destruction, but she was stopped by Celestia's divine nail.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "amount": 0,
                      "display_style": "card",
                      "ep_id": 7087,
                      "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/10/12/237301566/aa06aa829f5a3a926aef88750adb81f2_208058611950951154.png",
                      "menu_id": 20,
                      "name": "Ирминсуль",
                      "type": "custom_entry"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "Nibelung burned Irminsul in Natlan and destroyed its defenders, the",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "amount": 0,
                      "display_style": "text",
                      "ep_id": 7083,
                      "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/10/11/237301566/2aa6b47bf4316be4c736d48e07f765e4_1182305316823487314.png",
                      "menu_id": 23,
                      "name": "Ангелы",
                      "type": "custom_entry"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": ". Because of this, the Natlanese Ley Lines were greatly damaged, and the surviving angel",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "amount": 0,
                      "display_style": "text",
                      "ep_id": 7073,
                      "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/10/09/237301566/6b241f723a377795d5a2ef3c3e97200b_3435879319829205378.png",
                      "menu_id": 10,
                      "name": "Владыка Ночи",
                      "type": "custom_entry"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "created the Night Kingdom.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
